        <p>Welcome to the <strong>Daniel Can Fly</strong> website, surveys, and related research services. This Privacy Policy explains how <strong>HuaiHsuan Huang (Daniel Can Fly)</strong> collects, processes, uses, and protects your personal data.</p>

